 staff to consult with individuals and organizations informed on the subject of non-payment of child support to develop plans for the most effective career counseling opportunities for these individuals. Amends the Personnel Code. Provides that candidates who are alleged to have attempted deception or fraud in connection with an examination shall be afforded the opportunity to appeal and provide information to support their appeal which shall be considered when determining their eligibility as a candidate for employment. Makes further changes concerning the jurisdiction of the Department of Central Management Services with respect to selection and tenure on the basis of merit and fitness. Effective January 1, 2022.", "pending_committee_id": 0, "committee": [], "referrals": [{"date": "2021-02-22", "committee_id": 235, "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "name": "Rules"}, {"date": "2021-03-16", "committee_id": 2892, "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "name": "Labor & Commerce"}, {"date": "2021-04-28", "committee_id": 254, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "name": "Assignments"}, {"date": "2021-05-10", "committee_id": 277, "chamber": "S", "chamber_id": 36, "name": "Judiciary"}], "history": [{"date": "2021-02-19", "action": "Filed with the Clerk by Rep. Mary E. Flowers", "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2021-02-22", "action": "First Reading", "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2021-02-22", "action": "Referred to Rules Committee", "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2021-03-16", "action": "Assigned to Labor & Commerce Committee", "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2021-03-24", "action": "Do Pass / Short Debate Labor & Commerce Committee; 015-010-000", "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2021-04-08", "action": "Placed on Calendar 2nd Reading - Short Debate", "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2021-04-21", "action": 